Winter is over in South Africa and we've got just the thing for all the braai masters in the making to prepare for braai season. When you buy the Sunday Times at Pick n Pay on any Sunday in September, you'll get a free braai gift: Even better, if you then SMS the word BRAAI, your till-slip number and your name to 45476, you'll stand a chance of winning one of 10 Weber braais and Weber Classics braai books.